Walk%20On%20Moon%26quot%3B%3A%20Pragyan%20Rover%20Embarks%20On%2014-Day%20Lunar%20Mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20mission's%20Lander%20Module%20which%20touched%20down%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20has%20rolled%20out%20the%20rover%2C%20Pragyan%2C%20with%20ISRO%20saying%20%26quot%3BIndia%20took%20a%20walk%20on%20the%20moon%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20its%20official%20X%20handle%2C%20ISRO%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Brover%20ramped%20down.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BChandrayaan-3%20ROVER%3A%20Made%20in%20India--Made%20for%20the%20Moon!%20The%20Ch-3%20Rover%20ramped%20down%20from%20the%20lander%20and%20India%20took%20a%20walk%20on%20the%20moon!%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20Official%20sources%20had%20earlier%20confirmed%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnChandrayaan-3%20ROVER%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnMade%20in%20India%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%3Cbr%3E%5CnMade%20for%20the%20MOON%F0%9F%8C%96!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Ch-3%20Rover%20ramped%20down%20from%20the%20Lander%20and%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20took%20a%20walk%20on%20the%20moon%20!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMore%20updates%20soon.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan_3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan_3%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCh3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Ch3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1694545322251571687%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20congratulated%20the%20ISRO%20team%20for%20the%20successful%20deployment%20of%20Pragyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20rolling%20out%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20landing%20of%20Vikram%20marked%20the%20success%20of%20yet%20another%20stage%20of%20Chandrayaan%203.%20I%20look%20forward%20with%20excitement%2C%20alongside%20my%20fellow%20citizens%20and%20scientists%2C%20to%20the%20information%20and%20analyses%20that%20Pragyan%20will%20acquire%20and%20enrich%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20moon%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20precision%20landing%2C%20Chandrayaan%203's%20LM%20Vikram%20touched%20down%20the%20lunar%20surface%20at%206.04%20pm%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20sending%20the%20nation%20into%20wild%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%2026%20kg%20six-wheeled%20rover%20was%20scheduled%20to%20descend%20from%20the%20lander's%20belly%2C%20onto%20the%20Moon's%20surface%2C%20using%20one%20of%20its%20side%20panels%20as%20a%20ramp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20(Vikram)%20and%20rover%20(Pragyan)%20--%20with%20a%20total%20mass%20of%201%2C752%20kg%20--%20are%20designed%20to%20operate%20for%20one%20lunar%20daylight%20period%20(about%2014%20Earth%20days)%20to%20study%20the%20surroundings%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20ISRO%20officials%20do%20not%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20them%20coming%20to%20life%20for%20another%20lunar%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rover%20will%20carry%20out%20in-situ%20chemical%20analysis%20of%20the%20lunar%20surface%20during%20the%20course%20of%20its%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20lander%20and%20the%20rover%20have%20scientific%20payloads%20to%20carry%20out%20experiments%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rover%20would%20study%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20through%20its%20payloads%20APXS%20-%20Alpha%20Particle%20X-Ray%20Spectrometer%20-%20to%20derive%20the%20chemical%20composition%20and%20infer%20mineralogical%20composition%20to%20further%20enhance%20understanding%20of%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPragyan%20also%20has%20another%20payload--Laser%20Induced%20Breakdown%20Spectroscope%20(LIBS)%20to%20determine%20the%20elemental%20composition%20of%20lunar%20soil%20and%20rocks%20around%20the%20lunar%20landing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20Chairman%20S%20Somnath%20had%20earlier%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20powered%20descent%20(of%20lander)%20on%20to%20the%20landing%20site%2C%20there%20will%20be%20deployment%20of%20ramp%20and%20rover%20coming%20out.%20After%20this%20all%20the%20experiments%20will%20take%20place%20one%20after%20the%20other%20--%20all%20of%20which%20have%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20just%20one%20day%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20which%20is%2014%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692851400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftk24u1sg_rover-pragyan_650x400_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-made-in-india-made-for-moon-isros-tweet-as-pragyan-rover-begins-lunar-walk-4324375%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20mission's%20Lander%20Module%20which%20touched%20down%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20has%20rolled%20out%20the%20rover%2C%20Pragyan%2C%20with%20ISRO%20saying%20%26quot%3BIndia%20took%20a%20walk%20on%20the%20moon%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-made-in-india-made-for-moon-isros-tweet-as-pragyan-rover-begins-lunar-walk-4324375%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-made-in-india-made-for-moon-isros-tweet-as-pragyan-rover-begins-lunar-walk-4324375%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-made-in-india-made-for-moon-isros-tweet-as-pragyan-rover-begins-lunar-walk-4324375%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%