rst%20match%20had%20ended%20in%20a%20stalemate%20with%20just%20five%20more%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20players%20have%20cancelled%20each%20other%20out%20in%20the%20summit%20clash%20in%20Baku%2C%20but%20will%20have%20to%20alter%20their%20approach%20in%20the%20tie-breakers%20due%20to%20the%20time-sensitive%20nature%20of%20the%20format.%20Carlsen%20is%20already%20aware%20of%20what%20Praggnanandhaa%20can%20do%20in%20tie-breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPraggnanandhaa%20has%20already%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20tiebreaks%20against%20very%20strong%20players...%20I%20know%20he%20is%20very%20strong.%20If%20I%20have%20some%20energy%2C%20if%20I%20have%20a%20good%20day%2C%20obviously%20I%20will%20have%20good%20chances%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20tie-breaker%20games%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20tie-breaker%2C%20the%20two%20players%20will%20play%20two%20games%20in%20a%20rapid%20format%20with%20a%20time%20control%20of%2025%20minutes%20for%20each%20player%20and%20a%2010-second%20increment%20for%20each%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20they%20remain%20unseparated%2C%C2%A0then%20two%20more%20rapid%20games%20with%20a%20time%20control%20of%20'10%2B10'%20(10%20minutes%20for%20each%20player%20and%20a%2010-second%20increment%20for%20each%20move)%20will%20be%20played.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20winner%20is%20still%20not%20decided%20after%20tie-breakers%2C%20two%20more%20rapid%20games%20will%20be%20played%20with%20a%20time%20control%20of%205%20minutes%20and%20a%203-second%20increment%20for%20each%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEven%20if%20we%20don't%20find%20a%20winner%20after%20this%2C%20the%20title%20will%20be%20decided%20in%20a%20sudden-death%20mode%20with%20a%20single%20blitz%20game%20in%20the%20'3%2B2'%20format.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20second%20game%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20did%20not%20face%20any%20troubles%20with%20black%20pieces%2C%20with%20the%20players%20agreeing%20to%20a%20draw%20after%2030%20moves%20in%20an%20equal%20Bishop%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%2018-year-old%20Indian%20had%20stunned%20world%20No.%203%20Fabiano%20Caruana%20on%20Monday%20via%20the%20tie-break%20in%20the%20semifinals%20to%20set%20up%20a%20summit%20clash%20with%20Carlsen%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692851160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj40gh11o_r-praggnanandhaa-vs-magnus-carlsen-fide_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fr-praggnanandhaa-vs-magnus-carlsen-what-is-the-format-of-the-chess-world-cup-tie-breaker-4323068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20second%20game%2C%20R%20Praggnanandhaa%20did%20not%20face%20any%20troubles%20with%20black%20pieces%2C%20with%20the%20players%20agreeing%20to%20a%20draw%20after%2030%20moves%20in%20an%20equal%20Bishop%20ending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A243%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fr-praggnanandhaa-vs-magnus-carlsen-what-is-the-format-of-the-chess-world-cup-tie-breaker-4323068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fr-praggnanandhaa-vs-magnus-carlsen-what-is-the-format-of-the-chess-world-cup-tie-breaker-4323068%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fr-praggnanandhaa-vs-magnus-carlsen-what-is-the-format-of-the-chess-world-cup-tie-breaker-4323068%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20African%20News%20Website%20Says%20it%20Faced%20Cyber%20Attack%20After%20Publishing%20Report%20on%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24095258%2FF4I6NjYXQAEpKFx.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20South%20African%20news%20website%2C%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20subject%20to%20a%20cyber%20attack%20on%20Wednesday%20(August%2023)%20after%20publishing%20a%20report%20that%20said%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20unhappy%20not%20to%20be%20welcomed%20by%20his%20South%20African%20counterpart%20when%20he%20landed%2C%20and%20even%20refused%20to%20leave%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20publishing%2C%20Daily%20Maverick%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20a%20distributed%20denial%20of%20service%20(DDoS)%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdailymaverick%2Fstatus%2F1694409125906506203%5C%22%3Ethe%20publication%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9D%20A%20DDoS%20attack%20is%20described%20as%20a%20malicious%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20the%20normal%20traffic%20of%20a%20targeted%20server%2C%20network%20or%20website%20by%20overwhelming%20the%20target%20or%20its%20surrounding%20infrastructure%20with%20a%20flood%20of%20internet%20traffic%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20hours%20ago%2C%20the%20site%20suddenly%20went%20down.%20We%20picked%20it%20up%20very%20quickly%20and%20started%20identifying%20a%20massive%20distributed%20denial%20of%20service%20(DDoS)%20attack.%20We%20investigated%20and%20found%20it%20was%20coming%20from%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20Indian%20servers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20security%20coordinator%20at%2011%3A30%20pm%20IST%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20when%20Modi%20landed%20at%20the%20Waterkloof%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20leave%20the%20plane%20because%20a%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20rather%20than%20President%20Cyril%20Ramphosa%2C%20had%20come%20to%20welcome%20him.%20Ramphosa%2C%20however%2C%20did%20welcome%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20that%20though%20the%20attack%20was%20ongoing%2C%20the%20publication%20had%20managed%20to%20put%20a%20firewall%20in%20place%20and%20put%20the%20website%20back%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20obvious%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20attack%20is%20to%20deny%20the%20people%20of%20India%20access%20to%20this%20story%20as%20no%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20hide%20the%20source%20of%20the%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20editor-in-chief%20Branko%20Brkic%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20left%20us%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20block%20the%20entire%20domain%20of%20India%20to%20protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20site.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20is%20currently%20not%20accessible%20from%20India.%20%E2%80%9CDaily%20Maverick%20has%20been%20investigating%20ways%20to%20make%20the%20article%20accessible%20to%20India%20but%20the%20attack%20is%20so%20large%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20proving%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20publication%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20attempts%20and%20subsequent%20denials%20by%20Deputy%20President%20Paul%20Mashatile%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%20stands%20by%20its%20story%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20report%20on%20developments%2C%20Brkic%20continued.%20A%20spokesperson%20from%20Mashatile%E2%80%99s%20office%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsidhant%2Fstatus%2F1694366418475880575%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etold%20WION%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20aspect%20of%20what%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20is%20a%20lie%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20deputy%20president%20did%20not%20go%20to%20the%20airport%20to%20%E2%80%9Cappease%E2%80%9D%20Modi%2C%20but%20was%20there%20as%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20in%20South%20Africa%20to%20attend%20the%20BRICS%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692851053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2