n%20a%20childcare%20company%20which%20stood%20to%20benefit%20from%20new%20government%20policy%20but%20the%20failure%20was%20inadvertent%2C%20parliament's%20standards%20watchdog%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-breached-parliaments-code-of-conduct-inadvertently-report-4324139%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-breached-parliaments-code-of-conduct-inadvertently-report-4324139%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-pm-rishi-sunak-breached-parliaments-code-of-conduct-inadvertently-report-4324139%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Nation%20Celebrates%2C%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Lander-Rover%20Start%20Busy%20Day%20At%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-3%20made%20its%20historic%20touchdown%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20last%20evening%2C%20fulfilling%20the%20hopes%20of%201.4%20billion%20people%20and%20putting%20India%20into%20the%20elite%20space%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20country%20celebrates%20this%20huge%20milestone%2C%20the%20Vikram%20lander%20and%20Pragyan%20rover%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20do%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20The%20rover%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frover-pragyan-rolls-out-of-chandrayaan-3-lander-near-moons-south-pole-4323646%5C%22%3Ealready%20rolled%20onto%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20update%20this%20morning%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BChandrayaan-3%20ROVER%3A%20Made%20in%20India%20Made%20for%20the%20MOON!%20The%20Ch-3%20Rover%20ramped%20down%20from%20the%20Lander%20and%20India%20took%20a%20walk%20on%20the%20moon.%26quot%3B%20!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV's%20Pallava%20Bagla%20that%20both%20the%20lander%20and%20the%20rover%20are%20healthy%20and%20that%20Pragyan%20has%20rolled%20out%20of%20the%20Vikram%20lander.%20Images%20of%20the%20two%20may%20be%20released%20soon%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%2014%20days%2C%20the%20six-wheeled%20rover%20will%20carry%20out%20experiments%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon.%20Both%20Vikram%20lander%20and%20Pragyan%20rover%20have%20a%20mission%20life%20of%201%20lunar%20day%2C%20equal%20to%2014%20days%20on%20earth.%20The%20lander%20module%20is%20carrying%20five%20payloads%20for%20specific%20tasks%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rover's%20an%20Alpha%20Particle%20X-Ray%20Spectrometer%20will%20be%20used%20to%20derive%20the%20chemical%20composition%20and%20infer%20mineralogical%20composition%20to%20further%20enhance%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Laser%20Induced%20Breakdown%20Spectroscope%20will%20determine%20elemental%20composition%20of%20the%20lunar%20soil%20and%20rocks%20around%20the%20landing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lander%20is%20also%20carrying%20RAMBHA-LP%20(Langmuir%20Probe)%20to%20measure%20the%20near%20surface%20plasma%20(ions%20and%20electrons)%20density%20and%20its%20changes%20with%20time.%20ChaSTE%20Chandra's%20Surface%20Thermo%20Physical%20Experiment%20will%20carry%20out%20the%20measurements%20of%20thermal%20properties%20of%20lunar%20surface%20near%20its%20polar%20region.%20The%20Instrument%20for%20Lunar%20Seismic%20Activity%20will%20measure%20the%20seismicity%20around%20the%20landing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2014%20days%20of%20work%2C%20the%20activity%20of%20the%20solar%20energy-powered%20rover%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20slow%20down.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20it%20will%20be%20touch%20with%20the%20Lander%20Vikram%20that%20will%20relay%20data%20to%20ISRO.%20ISRO%20has%20no%20direct%20link%20with%20the%20rover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan%20mission%20has%20made%20India%20the%20first%20country%20to%20land%20a%20spacecraft%20near%20the%20moon's%20south%20pool%2C%20a%20region%20with%20frozen%20water%20that%20could%20be%20a%20source%20of%20oxygen%2C%20fuel%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692850620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F31h3dnb8_chandrayaan_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-chandrayaan-3-updates-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-pragyan-at-work-vikram-keeps-watch-busy-day-for-chandrayaan-3-duo-4324431%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chandrayaan-3%20made%20its%20historic%20touchdown%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20last%20evening%2C%20fulfilling%20the%20hopes%20of%201.4%20billion%20people%20and%20putting%20India%20into%20the%20elite%20space%20club.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-chandrayaan-3-updates-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-pragyan-at-work-vikram-keeps-watch-busy-day-for-chandrayaan-3-duo-4324431%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-chandrayaan-3-updates-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-pragyan-at-work-vikram-keeps-watch-busy-day-for-chandrayaan-3-duo-4324431%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-chandrayaan-3-updates-pragyan-rover-vikram-lander-pragyan-at-work-vikram-keeps-watch-busy-day-for-chandrayaan-3-duo-4324431%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant%20starts%20pumping%20radioactive%20wastewater%20into%20sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692850380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-japan-fukushima_6258657.jpg%3F20230822070147%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffukushima-nuclear-plant-starts-pumping-radioactive-wastewater-into-sea-1294624