to%20erase%20from%20its%20Preamble%20the%20terms%20secular%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98socialist%E2%80%99%20but%20to%20inscribe%20a%20new%20definition%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20as%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20done%20in%20ways%20by%20now%20characteristic%20and%20familiar%3A%20get%20religious%20pointmen%20to%20begin%20a%20grassroot%20propagation.%20Dhirendra%20Shastri%2C%20for%20instance%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwnEMq30q248%3Fsi%3DngO1d7w0V_J3vIJn%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F113764bf-dcea-4633-a4d5-53ab7423f8d6%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F113764bf-dcea-4633-a4d5-53ab7423f8d6%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692931796327000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1yjZG5XAsT-MjP72kL6iEi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enudge%20friendly%20%E2%80%98expert%E2%80%99%20voices%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20prod%20contention%20among%20the%20literati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20and%20perhaps%20the%20most%20infectious%20outreach%20is%20offered%20by%20comprador%20corporate-electronic%20media%20channels%20where%20a%20host%20of%20young%20anchors%20and%20reporters%20are%20now%20mentally%20primed%20to%20energetically%20project%20the%20virtues%20of%20official%20thinking.%20Often%2C%20all%20day%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agenda%20is%20being%20couched%20in%20converging%20ways%3A%20first%2C%20that%20the%20allegedly%20monochromatic%20cultural%20reality%20of%20this%20ancient%20land%20must%20find%20place%20as%20the%20informing%20principle%20of%20the%20political%20state%3B%20and%20then%2C%20by%20linking%20that%20in%20a%20most%20instructive%20marriage%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98giant%20strides%E2%80%99%20being%20made%20by%20the%20motherland%20in%20the%20universe%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20both%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20ostensibly%20requiring%20the%20drafting%20of%20a%20new%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20argument%20is%20mere%20chimeric%20fodder%20meant%20to%20entice%20the%20gawking%20nationalist%20base%2C%20high%20on%20pride%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20global%20leadership%20in%20order%20to%20obtain%20middle%20class%20assent%20on%20some%20spurious%20economic%20ground%20to%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20state%20into%20a%20strong%2C%20sectarian%20entity.%20Never%20mind%20the%20pathetic%20indices%20on%20hunger%20and%20malnutrition%2C%20record%20levels%20of%20unemployment%2C%20unconscionable%20inequalities%20of%20income%2C%20rampant%20anaemia%20among%20lactating%20women%2C%20the%20embarrassing%20need%20to%20feed%20free%20grains%20to%20some%2080%20crore%20Indians%2C%20a%20shameful%20per%20capita%20purchasing%20power%20parity%20ratio%20next%20to%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20developed%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBear%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20has%20already%20seen%20some%20106%20amendments%20in%2070%20years%2C%20while%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leading%20economy%2C%20the%20US%2C%20has%20made%20no%20more%20than%2027%20since%201787%3B%20the%20Japanese%20none%20at%20all%2C%20while%20the%20British%20do%20fine%20without%20a%20written%20constitution.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20least%20changes%20have%20taken%20place%20where%20development%20has%20been%20the%20highest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20much%2C%20thus%2C%20for%20the%20specious%20propaganda%20that%20rapid%20economic%20development%20requires%20a%20new%20constitution%20altogether.%20Not%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20but%20a%20congenial%20religio-cultural%20architecture%20requires%20the%20scrapping%20of%20the%20constitution%20as%20we%20now%20have%20it.%20And%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20corporate%20owners%20of%20the%20state%20love%20a%20circumstance%20in%20which%20sundry%20contentions%20among%20an%20unthinkingly%20consuming%20populace%20were%20put%20to%20final%20rest%20by%20a%20terminal%20sleight-of-hand%20such%20as%20a%20rewritten%20constitution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plain%20and%20telling%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20coming%20general%20election%20of%202024%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20India%E2%80%99s%20parallel%20to%20the%20German%20elections%20of%201933.%20Golwalkar%E2%80%99s%20lauding%20of%20the%20Nazi%20regime%20(see%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F3330b4ab-666c-4255-bb06-db6034ee99eb%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Flink.sbstck.com%2Fredirect%2F3330b4ab-666c-4255-bb06-db6034ee99eb%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1692931796327000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1-cQ7PhVjUmNMNck_Gqwl6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWe%2C%20Our%20Nationhood%20Defined%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%201938)%20remains%20a%20lodestar%20to%20remember%20as%20we%20conceptualise%20the%20menacing%20froth%20now%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20INDIA%20conglomerate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20while%20the%20coming%20together%20of%2026%20political%20parties%20into%20a%20conglomerate%20instructively%20captioned%20INDIA%2C%20is%20reflective%20of%20their%20understanding%20of%20the%20mortal%20nature%20of%20the%20prospect%20that%20now%20confronts%20the%20democratic%20republic%2C%20that%20understanding%20must%20attain%20to%20a%20recognition%20(an%20anagnorisis)%20that%20were%20