20an%20elite%20space%20club%20on%20Wednesday.%20India's%20moon%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20India%20thus%20has%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20land%20a%20rover%20on%20the%20moon%20after%20USSR%2FRussia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20China.%20India%20has%20become%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20land%20near%20the%20Moon's%20South%20Pole%2C%20which%20is%20the%20hot%20new%20destination%20since%20traces%20of%20water%20were%20detected%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20touchdown%20took%20place%20at%206.04%20pm%20amid%20huge%20cheers%20at%20the%20ISRO%20center%20in%20Bengaluru.%20%C2%A0Social%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20congratulatory%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20in%20the%20celebration%20was%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E's%20daughter%20Ziva.%20Dhoni's%20wife%20posted%20the%20video%20of%20her%20celebrating%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22cgcoqsk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcgcoqsk_ziva-chandrayaan_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22und%5C%22%3EZiva%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy4LfWAFpHg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fy4LfWAFpHg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20(%40Itzshreyas07)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FItzshreyas07%2Fstatus%2F1694330955199291496%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20live%20broadcast%20of%20the%20historic%20moment%20started%20at%205.20%20pm%20and%20the%20lander%20completed%20four%20stages%20before%20landing%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20of%20the%20stages%2C%20Vikram%20slowl