%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Feurope%2Flive-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-news-06-23-23%2Fh_8ca7869e3cd32d5f9f89d96fb2858f4b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20amount%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20mercenaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20tirade%2C%20Prigozhin%20said%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwagner-boss-prigozhin-russia-evil-defense-ministry-must-stop-2023-6%3Futm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dyahoo.com%5C%22%3E%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20stopped%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20individuals%20responsible%20for%20the%20death%20of%20Wagner%20fighters%20must%20be%20punished.%20Moscow's%20security%20services%20responded%20by%20announcing%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-open-criminal-case-against-wagner-boss-prigozhin-after-comments-2023-6%3Futm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dyahoo.com%5C%22%3E%20a%20criminal%20case%20against%20Prigozhin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20charging%20him%20with%20inciting%20an%20armed%20rebellion%20%E2%80%94%20a%20case%20which%20was%20later%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20day%20of%20Prigozhin's%20announcement%2C%20Wagner%20fighters%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimages-wagner-troops-descend-rostov-don-apparent-armed-rebellion-2023-6%3Futm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dyahoo.com%5C%22%3E%20captured%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20southern%20Russian%20city%20of%20Rostov-on-Don%2C%20a%20central%20command%20for%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20headed%20towards%20Moscow.%C2%A0Days%20later%2C%20Belarusian%20President%20Alexander%20Lukashenko%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbelarus-wants-wagner-commanders-help-improve-its-own-armed-forces-2023-6%3Finline-endstory-related-recommendations%3D%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dyahoo.com%5C%22%3E%20brokered%20a%20peace%20deal%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20forcing%20Prigozhin%20to%20call%20off%20the%20coup%20in%20exchange%20for%20immunity%20in%20Belarus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20mutiny%2C%20Prigozhin's%20exact%20whereabouts%20have%20been%20unknown.%C2%A0Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20he%20appeared%20in%20a%20video%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fprigozhin-video-africa-wagner-russia-rcna101130%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurported%20to%20be%20shot%20in%20Africa%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20Wagner%20troops%20have%20had%20a%20presence%20in%20several%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faviation-expert-breaks-down-yevgeny-prigozhin-crash-investigation-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692842724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6b03a912f290019aa2f00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faviation-expert-breaks-down-yevgeny-prigozhin-crash-investigation-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20aviation%20expert%20explained%20to%20Insider%20what%20immediately%20stood%20out%20in%20footage%20purporting%20to%20show%20Wagner%20boss%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin's%20plane%20crash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aharoun%40insider.com%20(Azmi%20Haroun)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faviation-expert-breaks-down-yevgeny-prigozhin-crash-investigation-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20Morari%20Bapu%20-%20What%20Their%20Meeting%20Means%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20in%20England%20is%20known%20for%20many%20things%20-%20its%20academic%20credentials%2C%20its%20world-class%20status%20of%20learning%2C%20its%20vibrant%20student%20life%20and%20its%20alums%20-%20the%20creme%20de%20la%20creme%20of%20global%20elites.%20But%20few%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20a%20recitation%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20in%20Cambridge%20would%20also%20generate%20global%20headlines.%20India's%20renowned%20spiritual%20leader%2C%20Morari%20Bapu%2C%20conducted%20a%20nine-day%20Ram%20Katha%20at%20Jesus%20College%2C%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20last%20week%2C%20and%20it%20saw%20the%20participation%20of%20Britain's%20first%20Hindu%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20on%20Independence%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%2C%20who%20has%20never%20been%20shy%20of%20his%20faith%2C%20spoke%20eloquently%20about%20how%20it%20guides%20him%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20jobs%20in%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20here%20today%20not%20as%20a%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20but%20as%20a%20Hindu%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sunak%20as%20he%20sought%20Bapu's%20blessings%20and%20underlined%20that%20his%20Hindu%20faith%20guides%20him%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20his%20life%20and%20gives%20him%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20his%20best%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Britain.%20He%20talked%20about%20how%20a%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20Ganesha%20sits%20gleefully%20on%20my%20desk%20at%2010%20Downing%20Street%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstant%20reminder%20to%20me%20about%20listening%20and%20reflecting%20on%20issues%20before%20acting%26quot%3B.%20Sunak%20even%20chanted%20%26quot%3BJai%20Siya%20Ram%26quot%3B%20and%20participated%20in%20an%20aarti%20on%20stage.%20Bapu's%20response%20has%20been%20equally%20warm%20as%20he%20underlined%20how%20%26quot%3Bthe%20humility%20with%20which%20PM%20Sunak%20approached%20the%20Vyaspeeth%20and%20conveyed%20his%20respect%20only%20underscores%20the%20virtues%20of%20his%20culture%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20has%20always%20been%20unequivocal%20in%20embracing%20his%20Hindu%20identity.%20As%20far%20back%20as%202017%2C%20he%20had%20declared%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20now%20a%20citizen%20of%20Britain.%20But%20my%20religion%20is%20Hindu.%20My%20religious%20and%20cultural%20heritage%20is%20Indian.%20I%20proudly%20say%20that%20I%20am%20a%20Hindu%20and%20my%20identity%20is%20also%20a%20Hindu.%26quot%3B%20He%20not%20only%20took%20his%20oath%20in%202020%20on%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%2C%20he%20has%20performed%20gau%20puja%20and%20has%20been%20seen%20wearing%20the%20kalawa%20(sacred%20red%20thread).%20He%20has%20celebrated%20Indian%20festivals%20like%20Diwali%20and%20Janmashtami%20with%20fervor.%20When%20Sunak%20as%20Chancellor%20had%20lit%20candles%20to%20mark%20Diwali%20on%20the%20doorstep%20of%20No%2011%20Downing%20Street%2C%20he%20had%20described%20it%20as%20one%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bproudest%20moments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20Sunak%20remains%20the%20favorite%20of%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20ethnic%20minorities%20in%20the%20country%2C%20coming%20close%20to%201.5%20million%20people.%20This%20diaspora%20is%20now%20also%20becoming%20politically%20conscious%20and%20in%20Sunak%20it%20sees%20its%20own%20rise%20as%20a%20confident%20self-assured%20constituency%20which%20is%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20shape%20the%20destiny%20of%20their%20nation%20more%20actively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak's%20rise%20is%20as%20much%20a%20tribute%20to%20his%20own%20grit%20and%20determination%20and%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20as%20it%20is%20to%20the%20rapidly%20evolving%20nature%20of%20the%20British%20politics.%20That%20the%20first%20ethnic%20minority%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20would%20be%20a%20Conservative%20would%20have%20been%20unthinkable%20just%20a%20few%20years%20back.%20But%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20has%20managed%20to%20modernize%20itself%20by%20reaching%20out%20to%20ethnic%20minorities%20in%20a%20sustained%20manner%20since%20the%20days%20of%20David%20Cameron%20and%20this%20has%20paid%20dividends.%20Sunak's%20comfort%20with%20his%20religious%20identity%20in%20some%20ways%20gels%20with%20values%20that%20the%20Tories%20hold%20dear%20-%20cultural%20rootedness.%20And%20his%20Prime%20Ministership%20has%20certainly%20brought%20some%20calm%20to%20the%20rank%20and%20file%20of%20the%20Tories%2C%20which%20was%20getting%20torn%20asunder%20by%20the%20shenanigans%20of%20Boris%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Conservatives%20are%20facing%20a%20tough%20political%20environment.%20Just%20a%20month%20back%2C%20Sunak's%20party%20took%20a%20beating%20and%20rival%20Labour%20Party%20and%20Liberal%20Democrats%20made%20some%20serious%20gains%20in%20the%20England%20local%20elections.%20The%20Tories%20also%20lost%20two%20safe%20seats%20in%20by-elections%20with%20huge%20margins%20to%20their%20political%20opponents%2C%20underscoring%20the%20deep%20electoral%20trouble%20the%20party%20finds%20itself%20in.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20spiraling%20and%20there%20is%20pessimism%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20British%20economy.%20The%20Tories%20are%20no%20longer%20seen%20as%20the%20party%20of%20governance%20with%20the%20famed%20British%20public%20services%20facing%20an%20all-round%20collapse.%20And%20the%20emotive%20issue%20of%20Brexit%20is%20no%20longer%20generating%20political%20dividend%20for%20the%20party.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20fast%20becoming%20a%20liability%20with%20some%20voters%20questioning%20how%20things%20could%20go%20this%20wrong%20so%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sunak%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tall%20order%20to%20build%20a%20winning%20coalition%20before%20next%20year's%20election.%20There%20are%20already%20predictions%20about%20the%20Tories%20facing%20a%20cataclysmic%20defeat%20in%20the%202024%20general%20election.%20Despite%20falling%20far%20behind%20the%20Labour%20Party%20in%20opinion%20polls%2C%20Sunak%20continues%20to%20maintain%20that%20the%20Conservatives%20can%20still%20win%20the%20next%20general%20election%20and%20that%20the%20next%20election%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bdone%20deal%26quot%3B%20for%20Labour.%20He%20has%20delineated%20five%20key%20priorities%20of%20his%20government%20-%20bringing%20down%20inflation%2C%20growing%20the%20economy%2C%20reducing%20debt%20and%20NHS%20waiting%20times%2C%20and%20stopping%20small%20boat%20crossings%20to%20control%20immigration.%20But%20he%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20deliver%20on%20most%20and%20time%20is%20running%20out%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20of%20Sunak's%20achievements%20so%20far%2C%20he%20faces%20tough%20political%20challenges%20ahead.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20times%20like%20these%20that%20faith%20becomes%20an%20anchor%2C%20helping%20to%20navigate%20the%20turbulence%20around%20and%20within.%20While%20his%20faith%20may%20be%20deeply%20personal%20for%20Sunak%2C%20its%20public%20demonstration%20is%20also%20a%20message%20to%20the%20wider%20Indian%20diaspora%20that%20its%20support%20will%20be%20key%20for%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20as%20he%20enters%20the%20last%20few%20difficult%20months%20of%20his%20premiership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692842400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fh5nk17uc_rishi-sunak-morari-bapu_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frishi-sunak-and-morari-bapu-what-their-meeting-means-4321357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20all%20of%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20achievements%20so%20far%2C%20he%20faces%20tough%20political%20challenges%20ahead.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20times%20like%20these%20that%20faith%20becomes%20an%20anchor%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fris