%20of%20three%20Gandhis%20%E2%80%93%20the%20mother%2C%20the%20son%20and%20the%20sister%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcong-appoints-new-working-committee-ahead-of-elections%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520new%2520working%2520committee%2520has%2Cex%252Dofficio%2520members%2520and%2520incharges.%5C%22%3Erejigged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20is%20a%20painful%20reminder%20of%20the%20persistence%20of%20a%20central%20dilemma%20in%20Indian%20politics%3A%20the%20continued%20dominance%20of%20the%20Gandhis%20in%20the%20Congress%20scheme%20of%20things%20provides%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20his%20most%20potent%20emotional%20appeal%20to%20the%20electorate%3B%20yet%2C%20no%20one%20%E2%80%93%20including%2C%20ironically%2C%20the%20family%20%E2%80%93%20knows%20what%20to%20do%20with%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdmittedly%2C%20the%20Modi%20strategists%20feel%20that%20if%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20then%20their%20man%20will%20happily%20laugh%20his%20way%20to%20the%20bank%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20are%20very%20many%2C%20including%20some%20very%20thoughtful%20and%20wise%20voices%2C%20who%20remain%20convinced%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20earned%20the%20spurs%20to%20position%20himself%20as%20the%20prime%20opponent%20of%20Modi.%20And%2C%20it%20is%20no%20rocket%20science%20to%20note%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-india-bloc-derek-obrien-karan-thapar%5C%22%3Eedifice%20of%20opposition%20unity%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20collapse%20if%20there%20is%20an%20insistence%20on%20making%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20the%20keystone%20of%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20most%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20Gandhis%20and%20their%20partisans%20tend%20to%20forget%20that%20the%20last%20time%20the%20Congress%20notched%20up%20a%20substantive%20performance%20at%20the%20national%20level%20was%20way%20back%20in%202009.%20The%20Congress%20had%20had%20a%20fine%20hour%2C%20after%20a%20long%20time.%20It%20was%20a%20unique%20achievement%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20crossing%20the%20200-mark%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%201991.%20What%20was%20most%20noteworthy%20about%20that%20battle%20%E2%80%93and%20this%20cannot%20be%20overemphasized%20%E2%80%93%20was%20that%20the%20Gandhis%20were%20seen%2C%20gladly%20and%20joyfully%2C%20campaigning%20for%20a%20non-Gandhi%20to%20become%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Not%20before%202009%20nor%20since%20have%20the%20Gandhis%20batted%20for%20someone%20from%20outside%20the%20family%20to%20take%20up%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20mantle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArguably%2C%20the%20country%20could%20have%20been%20spared%20a%20Narendra%20Modi%20tragedy%20had%20only%20the%20Gandhis%20learnt%20the%20correct%20lesson%20from%20the%202009%20vote.%20The%20voters%2C%20especially%20the%20influential%20middle%20classes%2C%20opted%20to%20endorse%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20stewardship%20because%20he%20represented%20stability%20and%20solidity.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20recall%20that%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20claim%20to%20get%20re-elected%20was%20presented%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20horrible%20Mumbai%20terror%20attack%20in%20November%202008%C2%A0%20and%20his%20own%20heart%20surgery%20a%20few%20months%20later.%20On%20both%20these%20counts%2C%20his%20leadership%20claims%20came%20under%20a%20cloud.%20Yet%20the%20voters%20made%20a%20clear%20choice%20between%20a%20cautious%20but%20competent%20consensus-seeking%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Eloh%20purush%3C%2Fem%3E%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20who%20promised%20a%20strong%2C%20%3Cem%3Edanda%3C%2Fem%3E%20government.%20The%20Manmohan%20Singh-Sonia%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%9Ccombo%E2%80%9D%20carried%20with%20it%20delicious%20a%20flavour%20%E2%80%93%20an%20honest%2C%20hard-working%20self-made%20man%2C%20offering%20his%20competence%20and%20experience%20in%20the%20service%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20being%20backed%20whole-heartedly%20by%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%2C%20with%20its%20own%20place%20in%20our%20collective%20imagination.%20The%20global%20community%20cheered%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20victory%20as%20a%20reaffirmation%20of%20meritocracy%20and%20educated%20leadership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20different%20story%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20a%20painful%20one%2C%20at%20that%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20Congress%2C%20especially%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20failed%20to%20appreciate%20the%20electorate%E2%80%99s%20wisdom%20and%20common%20sense.%20Instead%2C%20the%20top%20Congress%20leadership%20went%20into%20overdrive%20to%20undermine%20its%20own%20government%20and%20in%20the%20process%20ended%20up%20betraying%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20trust.%20And%20unthinkingly%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20the%20authoritarianism%20India%20is%20now%20suffering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tragedy%20is%20that%20no%20lessons%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20learnt%20from%20the%20last%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20defeats.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3Espeech%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20was%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-parliament-speech-manipur%5C%22%3Eself-absorbed%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20prime%20minister%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20in%20control%20of%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gaadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20can%20allow%20his%20megalomania%20to%20get%20the%20better%20of%20him%2C%20but%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20does%20not%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20using%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20forum%20for%20some%20kind%20of%20catharsis.%20Once%20again%2C%20the%20nation%20was%20given%20a%20good%20reason%20to%20conclude%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20sadly%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Gandhi%20would%20not%20do%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20Modi.%20The%20even%20bigger%20tragedy%20is%20that%20the%20Gandhis%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20understand%20that%20securing%20the%20country%20relief%20from%20Modi%20and%20all%20that%20he%20has%20come%20to%20represent%20is%20of%20far-greater%20relevance%20and%20importance%20than%20their%20own%20political%20prosperity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10214946%2Fimage-1211.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10214946%2Fimage-1211.png%20653w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F10214946%2Fimage-1211-300x134.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22291%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20August%2010%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20better%20or%20worse%2C%20the%20Modi%20political%20persona%20is%20cast%20in%20stone%3A%20the%20granite%20of%20arrogance%2C%20the%20sand%20of%20moral%20expedience%2C%20the%20slippery%20marble%20of%20political%20chicanery%2C%20all%20cemented%20with%20alternative%20layers%20of%20self-obsession%20and%20an%20inferiority%20complex.%20After%20ten%20years%20of%20self-proclaimed%20success%2C%20he%20feels%20no%20need%20to%20change.%20His%20handlers%20must%20be%20reminding%20him%20of%20the%20old%20Yankee%20advice%3A%20if%20it%20ain%E2%80%99t%20broke%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20fix%20it.%20In%20his%20two%20most%20recent%20speeches%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20from%20the%20Red%20Fort%2C%20Modi%20has%20left%20no%20one%20in%20doubt%20that%20it%20would%20be%20more%20of%20the%20same.%20Worse%2C%20another%20mandate%20would%20be%20read%20by%20his%20patrons%20and%20partisans%20as%20a%20license%20to%20overhaul%20the%20(Nehruvian)%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20polity%20is%20saddled%20with%20an%20unresolved%20dilemma.%20There%20is%20no%20sign%20of%20the%20Gandhis%20standing%20down.%20The%20other%20day%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%C2%A0son-in-law%20went%20public%20with%20his%20expectation%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20would%20have%20the%20good%20sense%20to%20send%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fleaders-react-to-robert-vadra-priyanka-gandhi-should-be-in-parliament-remark-2420532-2023-08-13%5C%22%3Ewife%20to%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Gandhis%E2%80%99%20chorus%20is%20prepared%20to%20full-throatedly%20sing%20%E2%80%9CRahul%20the%20messiah%2C%E2%80%9D%20even%20if%20it%20means%20performing%20in%20empty%20halls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20the%20Congress%20being%20in%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20seat%2C%20the%20opposition%20unity%20bandwagon%20will%20be%20stranded%20in%20irrelevance%20and%20unilateralism.%20But%20that%20driver%20cannot%20be%20a%20Gandhi.%20The%20country%20deserves%20a%20different%20choice%20than%20the%20one%20between%20the%20extremism%20of%20a%20pugnacious%20Modi%20and%20the%20extremism%20of%20an%20underbaked%20Rahul.%20The%20country%20needs%20moderation%2C%20sobriety%20and%20steadiness.%20Both%20Modi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20represent%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20recklessness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20onus%20is%20on%20the%20Gandhis.%20They%20have%20only%20one%20honourable%20course%20of%20action%20left%20ope