0of%20racketeering%2C%20Giuliani%20was%20also%20charged%20with%20solicitation%20of%20violation%20of%20oath%20by%20a%20public%20officer%2C%20false%20statements%20and%20writings%2C%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20impersonating%20a%20public%20officer%2C%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20forgery%20in%20the%20first%20degree%2C%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20false%20statements%20and%20writings%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20filing%20false%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Wednesday%20that%20he%20will%20plead%20not%20guilty%20to%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20same%20Rudy%20Giuliani%20that%20took%20down%20the%20mafia%2C%20that%20made%20New%20York%20City%20the%20safest%20city%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20in%20Georgia.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20degrade%20themselves%20by%20doing%20a%20mugshot%20of%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20feeling%20very%2C%20very%20good%20about%20it%20because%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20am%20defending%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20Americans%2C%20as%20I%20did%20so%20many%20times%20as%20a%20United%20States%20attorney%2C%26quot%3B%20Giuliani%2C%20who%20made%20a%20career%20out%20of%20prosecuting%20RICO%20cases%20before%20becoming%20a%20defendant%20in%20a%20RICO%20case%2C%20said%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20destroying%20my%20right%20to%20counsel%2C%20my%20right%20to%20be%20a%20lawyer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20seemingly%20referring%20to%20being%20prosecuted%20over%20allegations%20of%20crimes%20committed%20while%20serving%20as%20Trump's%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Washington%20DC%20ethics%20panel%20recently%20suggested%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-should-be-disbarred-dc-bar-ethics-panel-2023-7%5C%22%3EGiuliani%20be%20disbarred%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20actions%20after%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessins