%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20expansion%20issue%20had%20been%20discussed%20at%20the%20leaders%E2%80%99%20retreat%20on%20Tuesday%20evening.%20Indian%20official%20sources%20had%20said%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20development%E2%80%9D%2C%20claiming%20that%20India%20took%20the%20%E2%80%9Clead%20in%20forging%20consensus%20on%20membership%20criteria%20and%20selection%20of%20new%20members%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELong-standing%20proponents%20of%20the%20expansion%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20were%20quick%20to%20formally%20suggest%20a%20new%20moniker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20make%20good%20use%20of%20the%20BRICS%20Plus%20co-operation%20format%20and%20accelerate%20the%20expansion%20process%20to%20bring%20more%20countries%20into%20the%20family%2C%20to%20pool%20our%20strengths%20and%20wisdom%20to%20make%20global%20governance%20more%20just%20and%20equitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Xi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BRICS%20chair%2C%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%2C%20affirmed%20that%20there%20was%20universal%20consensus%20on%20expanding%20the%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20President%20Xi%2C%20you%20are%20in%20full%20support%20of%20the%20expansion%20of%20BRICS%20as%20has%20been%20articulated%20by%20all%20members%20that%20we%20stand%20at%20the%20cusp%20of%20expanding%20the%20BRICS%20family%20because%20it%20is%20through%20this%20expansion%20that%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20have%20a%20much%20stronger%20BRICS%20in%20these%20turbulent%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramaphosa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20await%20the%20decision%20that%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20leaders%20in%20this%20regard%20as%20we%20go%20on%20with%20our%20summit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20BRICS%20leaders%20had%20agreed%20that%20there%20would%20be%20an%20expansion%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20there%20was%20any%20agreement%20on%20the%20membership%20criteria%20%E2%80%93%20or%20if%20that%20has%20been%20left%20for%20future%20negotiations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20sources%20were%20clear%20that%20they%20would%20like%20to%20shape%20the%20membership%20criteria%20so%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CStrategic%20Partners%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20incorporated%20as%20new%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20South%20Africa%20had%20announced%20that%20around%2022%20countries%20had%20formally%20applied%20for%20membership%20of%20BRICS.%20The%20motivations%20of%20the%20countries%20ranged%20from%20getting%20preferred%20access%20to%20emerging%20markets%20to%20getting%20loans%20from%20BRICS%E2%80%99%20New%20Development%20Bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20the%20summit%20in%20person%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20speech%20through%20a%20video%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20took%20potshots%20at%20the%20West%20to%20justify%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022.%20%E2%80%9CRussia%20decided%20to%20support%20people%20that%20fight%20for%20their%20culture%2C%20for%20their%20traditions%2C%20for%20their%20language%2C%20and%20for%20their%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20Putin%2C%20the%20leaders%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20Brazil%20and%20China%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20and%20the%20need%20to%20find%20a%20peaceful%20solution%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Modi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20raise%20Ukraine%2C%20at%20least%20in%20his%20public%20remarks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPutin%20skipped%20the%20South%20Africa%20summit%20as%20otherwise%20Pretoria%20would%20have%20been%20obligated%20to%20arrest%20him%20ba