ce%20ministers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramaphosa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20president%20called%20for%20the%20BRICS%20Bank%20to%20be%20used%20to%20leverage%20change%20in%20the%20international%20financial%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20leverage%20the%20role%20of%20the%20New%20Development%20Bank%2C%20push%20forward%20reform%20of%20the%20international%20financial%20and%20monetary%20systems%20and%20increase%20the%20representation%20and%20voice%20of%20developing%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutreach%20dinner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20day%20ended%20with%20a%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20South%20Africa%20for%20all%20the%20heads%20of%20state%20who%20had%20travelled%20from%20across%20the%20African%20continent%20and%20beyond.%20While%20South%20Africa%20had%20invited%20over%2060%20countries%2C%20the%20final%20tally%20was%20around%2040%20leaders%20in%20Johannesburg.%20Many%20of%20them%20were%20also%20visiting%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20China-Africa%20forum%2C%20which%20is%20again%20being%20organised%20by%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Modi%20will%20attend%20two%20sessions%20of%20the%20BRICS%20Africa%20outreach%20and%20BRICS%20plus%20dialogue.%20In%20between%2C%20there%20is%20a%20window%20of%20about%20four%20hours%20for%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20to%20have%20a%20series%20of%20bilateral%20meetings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20still%20not%20known%20whether%20Modi%20will%20meet%20with%20Xi%20in%20a%20separate%20bilateral%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit.%20Modi%20is%20scheduled%20to%20leave%20South%20Africa%20on%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692816598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24001805%2FF4NKlFIWcAAT_Qt.jpeg%22%2C%22originID