on.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20what%20is%20a%20further%20shrinking%20in%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20to%20be%20used%20to%20nurture%20a%20climate%20of%20information%2C%20access%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20country%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20records%20of%20lakhs%20of%20previous%20RTI%20applications%20have%20vanished%20from%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20RTIOnline%20portal.%20An%20activist%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20amounts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremoving%20government%20orders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERTIOnline%20is%20the%20platform%20through%20which%20citizens%20can%20file%20for%20access%20to%20public%20information%20and%20record%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fyears-of-data-goes-missing-from-union-governments-rti-portal%2Farticle67226969.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cviewed%20and%20verified%20samples%20of%20applications%20from%20two%20RTI%20activists%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20has%20had%20their%20entire%20account%20purged%20of%20information%20from%20before%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandra%20Shekhar%20Gaur%2C%20an%20RTI%20activist%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mismatch%20of%20several%20hundreds%20in%20his%20account.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%2C%20a%20digital%20rights%20activist%20and%20columnist%20on%20digital%20issues%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20confirmed%20the%20disappearance.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20RTI%20Online%20portal%20was%20being%20turned%20unusable%20by%20the%20government%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months%20with%20them%20stopping%20new%20registrations%20and%20even%20warning%20of%20deleting%20accounts%20that%20are%20not%20being%20used.%20Now%20All%20the%20RTIs%20filed%20prior%20to%202019%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20server.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20this%20was%20as%20serious%20as%20removing%20government%20orders.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20official%20intimation%20about%20it%20to%20any%20of%20the%20RTI%20portal%20users%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%2C%20which%20administers%20the%20portal%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20query%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20missing%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20senior%20rights%20and%20transparency%20activist%20Anjali%20Bhardwaj%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20extremely%20regressive%20move.%20All%20RTIs%20and%20replies%20should%20have%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20been%20made%20public%2C%20as%20also%20mandated%20by%20the%20DoPT.%20It%20might%20be%20useful%20to%20understand%20if%20they%20have%20been%20deleted%20permanently%20or%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20accessible%20on%20the%20portal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20deletion%20on%20the%20portal%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20staggering%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20calculates%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20RTIOnline%20portal%20has%20processed%20over%2058.3%20lakh%20applications%20from%202013%2C%20when%20it%20was%20launched%2C%20to%202022.%20The%20number%20of%20applications%20filed%20has%20been%20growing%20steadily%2C%20with%20over%2012.6%20lakh%20applications%20filed%20in%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20site%20had%20been%20behaving%20sub-optimally%20and%20poorly%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20portal%20has%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Eat%20least%20two%20periods%20of%20multiple%20days%E2%80%A6%3Cspan%3E%20lagged%20in%20speed%20and%20performance%2C%20and%20applications%20were%20not%20filed%20with%20authorities%20until%20days%20after%20users%20made%20a%20payment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%20was%20a%20landmark%20law%20in%20India%20that%20empowered%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20demand%20public%20information%20and%20inverted%20the%20relationship%20of%20staid%20bureaucracies%20and%20opaque%20governments%2C%20opening%20them%20up%20to%20scrutiny.%20But%20ever%20since%202014%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20get%20information%20through%20applications%2C%20or%20in%20appeal%2C%20has%20been%20hampered%20by%20an%20air%20of%20unwillingness%20in%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20and%20often%20the%20non-appointment%20of%20Information%20Commissioners%20for%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20passage%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20last%20session%20of%20parliament%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewill%20amount%20to%20amending%20the%20RTI%20Act%20through%20the%20backdoor%2C%20experts%20have%20said.%20The%20Bill%20has%20since%20been%20signed%20into%20law.%20Earlier%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgovernment-severely-restricting-rti-act-through-data-bill-ncpri%2Farticle67080300.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20larger%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20justified%20the%20disclosure%20of%20personal%20information.%20Now%2C%20the%20new%20data%20Bill%20prohibits%20government%20agencies%20from%20sharing%20private%20information%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20public%20interest%20it%20may%20entail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publishe