frican-news-site-alleges-cyber-attack-from-india%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20website%20was%20subject%20to%20Distributed%20Denial-of-Service%20(DDoS)%20attacks%20from%20India.%20DDoS%20attacks%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cloudflare.com%2Fen-in%2Flearning%2Fddos%2Fwhat-is-a-ddos-attack%2F%5C%22%3Emalicious%20attempts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20overwhelm%20a%20website%20or%20its%20surrounding%20infrastructure%20with%20a%20flood%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Indian%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20not%20officially%20commented%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20article%2C%20official%20sources%20have%20denied%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20also%20says%20that%20the%20South%20African%20government%20arranged%20for%20Xi%20to%20make%20a%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20country%20before%20the%20BRICS%20summit%2C%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20Modi%20due%20to%20scheduling%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESA%20officials%20deny%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20another%20South%20African%20news%20outlet%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news24.com%2Fnews24%2Fpolitics%2Fsa-pours-cold-water-on-modis-alleged-refusal-to-disembark-plane-when-welcomed-by-minister-20230823%5C%22%3Enews24%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reported%20that%20government%20officials%20strongly%20denied%20the%20claims%20made%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EDaily%20Maverick%3C%2Fem%3E%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20International%20Relations%20and%20Cooperation%20(Dirco)%2C%20Lunga%20Ngqengelele%20said%20the%20South%20African%20government%20had%20%E2%80%9Carranged%20with%20its%20BRICS%20counterparts%20as%20to%20who%20would%20receive%20the%20respective%20heads%20of%20state%20at%20the%20Sandton%20Convention%20Centre%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20was%20no%20tension%20from%20the%20Indian%20representatives%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccommon%20for%20ministers%20to%20welcome%20heads%20of%20state%20during%20working%20visits%E2%80%9D.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20foreign%20minister%20Naledi%20Pandor%20had%20received%20Brazil%E2%80%99s%20President%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20with%20no%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Indian%20government%20knew%20who%20would%20have%20received%20the%20prime%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20cases%2C%20it%20is%20ministers%20who%20receive%20heads%20of%20state%20%5Bduring%20working%20visits%5D%2C%20or%20the%20president%20himself%2C%20if%20he%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20African%20vice%20president%20Mashatile%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%20Vukani%20Mde%20also%20denied%20the%20%3Cem%3EMaverick%3C%2Fem%3E%20story.%20He%20said%20Mashatile%E2%80%99s%20office%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20well%20aware%2C%20ahead%20of%20time%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20would%20be%20arriving%20and%20that%20he%20would%20be%20receiving%20him.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20there%20well%20before%20PM%20Modi%20landed%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMde%20also%20denied%20the%20claim%20that%20Mashatile%20had%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdispatched%E2%80%9D%20from%20an%20event%20%E2%80%93%20saying%20that%20he%20finished%20his%20duties%20so%20that%20he%20could%20go%20to%20Waterkloof%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20not%20%E2%80%98dispatched%E2%80%99%20suddenly%2C%20he%20did%20not%20need%20to%20%E2%80%98appease%E2%80%99%20anyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20news24%20report%20says%20President%20Ramaphosa%20managed%20the%20%E2%80%9Capparent%20tensions%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Indian%20delegation%20by%20first%20greeting%20Modi%20during%20a%20photo%20opportunity%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20%E2%80%9Cbefore%20the%20other%20BRICS%20leaders%20arrived%2C%20and%20after%20he%20and%20Modi%20had%20met%20for%20a%