age%2C%20she%20would%20make%20the%20effort%20to%20learn%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20loved%20hearing%20people%20speak%20different%20languages.%20But%20when%20my%20stepfamily%20spoke%20Serbian%20at%20home%2C%20instead%20of%20learning%20it%2C%20my%20dad%20would%20leave%20the%20room.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20that%20if%20I%20met%20someone%20from%20a%20different%20culture%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20learn%20their%20language%2C%20which%20would%20be%20good%20for%20us%20and%20our%20family%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Elizabeth%20Marie%20Keyton%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20linguaphile%20started%20her%20career%20as%20an%20English%20teacher%20in%20South%20Korea%20when%20she%20was%2021.%20She%20travelled%20to%20countries%20like%20UAE%20and%20Vietnam%20teaching%20English%20as%20a%20second%20language%20(ESL).%20It%20was%20in%20the%20UAE%20that%20she%20had%20her%20first%20brush%20with%20Malayalam%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20large%20number%20of%20Malayalis%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometime%20in%202017%2C%20she%20met%20her%20now%20husband%20Arjun%2C%20a%20Malayali%2C%20in%20Dubai.%20This%20eventually%20birthed%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98Elikutty%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Malayalam%20teaching%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Felizabeth-1692799075.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elizabeth%20teaches%20Malayalam%20through%20her%20Instagram%20page%20eli.kutty%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Felizabeth-1692799075.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Felizabeth-1692799075-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Felizabeth-1692799075-500