hat%20terrorists%20were%20attempting%20to%20cross%20the%20LoC.%20Alert%20troops%20engaged%20them%20with%20effective%20fire%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20flee%20their%20ambush%20sites%20due%20to%20inclement%20weather%20and%20terrain.%20One%20terrorist%20fell%20and%20was%20injured%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20recovery%20of%20weapons%20and%20Pakistani%20medicines%2C%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20injuries%2C%20the%20terrorists%20managed%20to%20cross%20the%20LoC%20but%20eventually%20succumbed%20to%20their%20injuries%2C%20according%20to%20Bartwal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKohli%E2%80%99s%20original%20article%20came%20with%20a%20disclaimer%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20the%20military%20has%20not%20yet%20confirmed%20the%20surgical%20strike.%20It%20cited%20unnamed%20sources%20within%20the%20military%20who%20indicated%20to%20him%20that%20the%20operation%20was%20carried%20out%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20darkness.%20The%20article%20implied%20that%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20indicative%20of%20their%20unease%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20previous%20incidents%20such%20as%20the%20Balakot%20airstrike%20and%20the%20Uri%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20article%20claimed%20the%20operation%20caught%20the%20terrorists%20off%20guard%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20no%20time%20to%20react.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArmy%20PRO%20Lt%20Col%20Bartwal%20has%20categorically%20denied%20the%20article%E2%80%99s%20contents.%20The%20information%20published%20lacks%20credibility%20and%20has%20not%20been%20validated%20by%20any%20official%20source%2C%20Bartwal%20is%20quoted%20as%20having%20said%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F08%2F22%2Fhow-dainik-jagran-manufactured-a-surgical-strike-by-the-indian-army-in-pok%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20article.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20questioned%20about%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20denial%2C%20Kohli%20said%20he%20could%20provide%20visual%20evidence%20in%20support%20of%20his%20claims%20if%20required.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%202020%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20mechanisms%20to%20address%20fake%20news%20and%20misinformation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20introduced%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20last%20parliament%20session%20says%20that%20disseminating%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20news%20or%20misleading%20information%E2%80%9D%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%20three%20years%20in%20prison.%20It%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20for%20assessment.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20IT%20Rules%2C%202023%2C%20which%20are%20often%20criticised%20for%20giving%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessnow.org%2Fpress-release%2Fwithdraw-india-it-rules%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernment%20arbitrary%2C%20overbroad%2C%20and%20unchecked%20censorship%20powers%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20purport%20to%20have%20the%20broad%20aim%20of%20reducing%20fake%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20army%20has%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Jagran%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20editor-in-chief%20Sanjay%20Gupta%20and%20has%20%E2%80%9Cwarned%E2%80%9D%20the%20publication%20to%20not%20repeat%20such%20a%20thing%20and%20said%20the%20matter%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20be%20escalated%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%2C%E2%80%9D%20if%20it%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692799140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F23192806%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Farmy-dainik-jagran-pib-surgical-strike%22%2C%22