%20emerging%20technology%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20digital%2Fhuman%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IFF%2C%20which%20advocates%20for%20digital%20rights%20and%20online%20freedoms%20in%20India%2C%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20at%20the%20India%20International%20Centre%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lodhi%20Estate%20area%2C%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20sessions%2C%20each%20with%20a%20different%20set%20of%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESession%201%20is%20an%20unmoderated%20discussion%20between%20researcher%20%3Cspan%3EShivangi%20Narayan%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20journalist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESamarth%20Bansal%3C%2Fspan%3E%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnon-artificial%20consequences%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%E2%80%9D%20on%20digital%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPossible%20topics%20up%20for%20discussion%20here%20are%20the%20challenges%20associated%20with%20generative%20AI%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20large%20language%20models%20and%20text-to-image%20models%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20need%20for%20accountability%20among%20big%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESession%202%20is%20a%20panel%20discussion%20between%20ICRIER%20senior%20fellow%20%3Cspan%3EMansi%20Kedia%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Quantum%20Hub%20co-founder%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMedianama%3C%2Fem%3E%20founder%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENikhil%20Pahwa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20titled%20%E2%80%9CHow%20public%20are%20digital%20public%20infrastructures%3F%E2%80%9D%20It%20will%20be%20moderated%20by%20journalist%20Aditi%20Agrawal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20session%20is%20another%20unmoderated%20discussion%20and%20is%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3ECaste%2C%20data%20privacy%2C%20and%20digital%20technologies%E2%80%9D.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeaturing%20author%20Manoj%20Mitta%20and%20lawyer%20Nikita%20Sonavane%2C%20the%20IFF%20said%20this%20discussion%20%E2%80%9C%3Cspan%3Ewill%20seek%20to%20investigate%20the%20intricate%20relationship%20between%20technology%20and%20caste%20dynamics.%20It%20will%20also%20examine%20the%20influence%20of%20caste%20dynamics%20on%20our%20experiences%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20vice%20versa.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMitta%20has%20recently%20authored%20the%20book%C2%A0%3Cem%3ECaste%20Pride%3A%20Battles%20for%20Equality%20in%20Hindu%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20You%20can%20read%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbanaras-kashi-vishwanath-harijans-temple-entry%5C%22%3Eexcerpt%20from%20his%20book%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20media%20partner%20for%20%E2%80%98Privacy%20Supreme%E2%80%99%20and%20will%20cover%20the%20event%20tomorrow%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPrivacySupreme%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PrivacySupreme%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20back%2C%20and%20we%20are%20delighted%20to%20be%20a%20media%20partner!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrate%20the%20six%20years%20of%20the%20Puttaswamy%20judgement%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Finternetfreedom%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40internetfreedom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20stellar%20lineup%20of%20speakers%20on%20August%2024%20at%20India%20International%20Centre%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegister%20Now%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4HuBAbpV4l%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4HuBAbpV4l%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FEIaK500sgG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FEIaK500sgG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20Wire%20(%40thewire_in)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthewire_in%2Fstatus%2F1694311020691333194%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3