20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%20sport.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20a%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%20attracted%20big%20money%20corporate%20sponsorship%20and%20was%20watched%20eagerly%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20play%20was%20flowing%20and%20exciting%20to%20watch.%20Football%2C%20so%20often%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98beautiful%20game%E2%80%99%2C%20lived%20up%20to%20that%20description.%20A%20sport%20which%20has%20so%20often%20been%20vulgar%20and%20sexist%20has%20been%20in%20part%20redeemed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20fully%20half-a-century%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20was%20banned%20in%20England.%20The%20women%E2%80%99s%20game%20developed%20in%20the%201880s%2C%20and%20some%20early%20matches%20attracted%20a%20crowd%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands.%20But%20in%201921%20the%20Football%20Association%20outlawed%20the%20use%20of%20any%20of%20its%20grounds%20and%20facilities%20for%20women%20declaring%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20game%20of%20football%20is%20quite%20unsuitable%20for%20females%20and%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20encouraged%E2%80%99.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20football%20withered%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ban%20was%20only%20lifted%20in%201970.%20And%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Super%20League%20%E2%80%93%20the%20top%20tier%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20football%20in%20England%2C%20with%2012%20professional%20teams%20%E2%80%93%20was%20established%20as%20recently%20as%202010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fseven-ways-fifa-world-cup-move-dial-womens-sport%5C%22%3ESeven%20Ways%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20Can%20Move%20the%20Dial%20on%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Sport%20Forever%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAttendances%20at%20women%E2%80%99s%20games%20are%20not%20as%20high%20as%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20Premier%20League%3B%20transfer%20fees%20and%20salaries%20are%20more%20modest.%20But%20that%20is%20starting%20to%20chan