udy%20in%20madrasas%20or%20work%20as%20imams%3F%20Can%20they%20take%20such%20a%20step%20out%20of%20fear%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20I%20do%20not%20call%20it%20fear%20among%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20my%20biggest%20concern%20is%3A%20can%20I%20one%20day%20be%20recognised%20as%20a%20Muslim%20too%3F%20That%20is%20going%20to%20be%20dangerous.%20Few%20people%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20this%20fear.%20Many%20Muslims%20have%20started%20keeping%20their%20religious%20identity%20hidden%20behind%20the%20cover%20of%20silence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMuslims%20feel%20that%20whenever%20they%20are%20or%20will%20be%20targeted%20for%20their%20religion%2C%20neither%20anyone%20from%20other%20communities%20nor%20even%20the%20police%20will%20come%20to%20their%20rescue.%20I%20could%20talk%20about%20hope%2C%20but%20the%20way%20the%20state%20has%20patronised%20hatred%20and%20the%20way%20slogans%20of%20genocide%20are%20raised%20in%20%3Cem%3Edharam%20sansads%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20hope%20visible.%20The%20Muslim%20community%20has%20been%20put%20to%20sacrifice%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAn%20asterisk%20indicates%20that%20the%20person%E2%80%99s%20name%20has%20been%20changed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F255744%2Ffears-of-indian-muslims-in-new-india%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%20Hindi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It%20was%20translated%20into%20English%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692790205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F04201314%2FIMG_2127.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwide-range-of-fears-new-indias-muslims-have%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20systematic%20effort%20is%20on%20to%20isolate%20Muslims%20at%20more%20or%20less%20every%20level%20of%20our%20society.