i%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20has%20expressed%20strong%20concern%20over%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20recent%20attempts%20to%20suppress%20media%20voices%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20including%20the%20freezing%20of%20Facebook%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20accounts%20of%20Gaon%20Savera%2C%20a%20digital%20media%20platform%20that%20advocates%20for%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20amid%20agitations%20by%20farmers%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab%20against%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20governments%20and%20a%20forthcoming%C2%A0%20national%20convention%20of%20workers%20and%20peasants%20Delhi%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20on%20August%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaon%20Savera%2C%20led%20by%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%2C%20provides%20news%20and%20perspectives%20on%20rural%20life%20and%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mainstream%20media%20has%20largely%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20demonstrations%20by%20farmers%20and%20their%20demands.%20Now%2C%20even%20small%20independent%20platforms%20such%20as%20Gaon-Savera%20that%20take%20a%20pro%20farmers%20and%20pro%20people%20stand%20are%20being%20targeted.%20Along%20with%20Gaon%20Savera%2C%20the%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20many%20farmer%20leaders%20have%20also%20been%20frozen%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20also%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20freezing%20of%20the%20website%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Srinagar-based%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20the%20Kashmir%20website%E2%80%99s%20editor%20Fahad%20Shah%20had%20already%20been%20arrested%20in%20February%202022%2C%20and%20had%20been%20charged%20under%20UAPA%2C%20and%20languishes%20in%20jail.%20A%20former%20trainee%20reporter%20Sajad%20Gul%20is%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClosing%20down%20news%20portals%2C%20YouTube%20channels%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%20is%20becoming%20a%20common%20tactic%20by%20governments%2C%20both%20in%20the%20states%20and%20at%20the%20centre.%20Prolonged%20internet%20bans%2C%20as%20in%20Manipur%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20are%20also%20becoming%20common.%20India%20is%20becoming%20infamous%20as%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20deliberate%20disruptions%20of%20the%20internet.%20The%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20calls%20for%20an%20end%20to%20all%20such%20arbitrary%20practices%20that%20bode%20ill%20for%20a%20free%20media%20and%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20press%20release%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%20registers%20its%20strong%20protest%20at%20the%20repeated%20moves%20to%20muffle%20media%20voices%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%20the%20Facebook%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20accounts%20of%20Gaon%20Savera%2C%20a%20prominent%20digital%20media%20platform%20that%20voices%20issues%20of%20farmers%2C%20were%20frozen%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20The%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20amid%20agitations%20by%20farmers%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab%20against%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20governments%20and%20a%20national%20convention%20of%20workers%20and%20peasants%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Delhi%20on%20August%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaon%20Savera%20is%20a%20multi-media%20outlet%20run%20by%20a%20young%20journalist%2C%20Mandeep%20Punia%2C%20who%20in%20the%20past%20was%20arrested%20for%20covering%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%20in%20the%20Tikri%2C%20Singhu%20and%20Ghazipur%20borders%20of%20Delhi.%20His%20media%20outlet%20carries%20news%20and%20views%20on%20village%20life%20and%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%20has%20larg