ewheeling%20chat%20on%20Bombay%20of%20yore%2C%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20and%20how%20he%20inspired%20his%20love%20for%20music.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%2C%C2%A0Mehta%20significantly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ftimes-of-india-removed-quote-on-wanting-peace-for-indian-muslims-from-interview-zubin-mehta%5C%22%3Ealleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Times%20of%20India%3Cem%3E%20had%20removed%20just%20one%20line%20from%20an%20interview%20he%20recently%20gave%20to%20the%20newspaper%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20he%20wishes%20Muslims%20in%20India%20are%20able%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20forever.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20on%20this%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Ftimes-of-india-removed-quote-on-wanting-peace-for-indian-muslims-from-interview-zubin-mehta%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20this%20interview%20is%20given%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Good%20evening%2C%20ladies%20and%20gentlemen.%20Before%20I%20begin%20my%20conversation%20with%20Mr%20Mehta%2C%20let%20me%20say%20that%20magical%20music%20performance%20is%20living%20proof%20that%20the%20spirit%20of%20India%20survived%202014.%20And%20this%20young%20generation%2C%20this%20young%20generation%20will%20keep%20the%20spirit%20of%20India%20alive%20no%20matter%20who%20rules%20us%20or%20for%20how%20long%20they%20rule%20us.%20And%20can%20I%20add%2C%20sir%2C%20your%20father%20would%20have%20been%20looking%20down%20from%20heaven%20smiling%20and%20he%20would%20have%20said%20to%20himself%20these%20children%20have%20given%20my%20Foundation%20life%2C%20meaning%2C%20and%20specific%20beauty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20thank%20you.%20That%20was%20the%20most%20magnificent%20thing%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20Ladies%20and%20gentlemen%2C%20before%20I%20actually%20start%20talking%20to%20Mr%20Mehta%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20a%20story%20about%20the%20very%20first%20time%20I%20met%20him.%20He%20won%E2%80%99t%20remember%2C%20I%20can%20promise%20you.%20It%20was%2030%20years%20ago%2C%201994-95%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20come%2C%20sir%2C%20with%20the%20Israeli%20Philharmonic%20Orchestra%2C%20and%20in%20those%20days%20there%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20private%20television%20in%20India.%20There%20was%20no%20independent%20television.%20We%20would%20make%20programs%20on%20videos%2C%20and%20the%20one%20I%20worked%20on%20was%20called%20%E2%80%98Eyewitness%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoordarshan%20got%20in%20touch%20and%20said%20could%20we%20collaborate%20to%20do%20an%20interview%20with%20Mr%20Mehta%2C%C2%A0%20and%20I%20said%20of%20course%20it%20would%20be%20a%20pleasure.%20And%20since%20it%20was%20Doordarshan%E2%80%99s%20idea%2C%20the%20interview%20was%20arranged%20and%20fixed%20by%20them.%20And%20they%20chose%20nine%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20I%20said%20to%20myself%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20ungodly%20hour%20of%20the%20day!%20But%20since%20Mr%20Mehta%20has%20agreed%2C%20nine%20in%20the%20morning%20it%20is.%20And%20then%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20night%20before%20was%20your%20grand%20performance%20in%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20said%20he%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20have%20a%20very%20short%20night%20of%20sleep%20before%20he%20comes%20to%20me.%20So%20we%20arrived%2C%20we%20set%20up%2C%20the%20crew%20and%20I%20were%20ready%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20the%20Meridian%20Hotel%20where%20you%20were%20staying.%20And%20they%E2%80%99d%20given%20us%20a%20room%20for%20the%20recording%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20corridor%20from%20your%20suite.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20at%208.30%20we%20were%20ready%2C%20and%20we%20waited.%209%20o%E2%80%99clock%20came%20but%20Mr%20Mehta%20didn%E2%80%99t.%209.15%20c