s%20their%20concern%20about%20finding%20a%20market%20for%20their%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20relief%20for%20farmers%20because%20lugging%20quintals%20of%20millet%20across%20state%20lines%20to%20sell%20is%20not%20a%20wise%20option.%20He%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20farmers%20bring%20the%20millets%20to%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20give%20them%20the%20promised%20MSP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20factory%2C%20local%20women%20from%20the%20village%20participate%20in%20the%20cleaning%20and%20segregating%20process.%20Once%20they%20deem%20the%20quality%20fit%2C%20the%20millets%20are%20processed%20into%20value-added%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosa%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20millet%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20malt%2C%20etc.%20These%20products%20are%20sold%20through%20Amazon%20and%20priced%20nominally%20at%20Rs%20150%20upwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomashekar%20also%20shares%20that%20their%20association%20with%20farmers%20goes%20beyond%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314758%2Fmothers-start-rigdam-foods-ready-to-eat-millet-snacks-for-children-earn-turnover-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiving%20them%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helping%20them%20find%20a%20market%20for%20their%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20assist%20families%20affected%20by%20farmer%20suicides%20by%20providing%20sewing%20machines%2C%20livestock%2C%20and%20other%20resources%20that%20can%20help%20them%20earn%20a%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20harvested%20millets%20are%20processed%20at%20the%20factory%20after%20which%20they%20are%20turned%20into%20products%20like%20dosas%20and%20malts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Ffarming-3-1692019102-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20harvested%20millets%20are%20processed%20at%20the%20factory%20after%20which%20they%20are%20turned%20into%20products%20like%20dosa%20mixes%20and%20malts%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Somashekar%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Hemadri%20Reddy%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Kodumur%20village%20has%20been%20cultivating%20brown%20top%20millet%20since%20his%20association%20with%20Adithi%20Millets%20in%20June%202022.%20Sharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20joining%20Adithi%20Millets%2C%20I%20would%20sow%20the%20seeds%20of%20brown%20top%20millet%20in%20four%20acres%20and%20get%204%2C000%20kg%20millets.%20When%20I%20would%20sell%20it%20in%20the%20market%2C%20I%20would%20get%20an%20MSP%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20quintal%20and%20earn%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20the%20entire%20harvest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20joining%20Adithi%20Millets%20the%20farmer%20adopted%20Somashekar%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2F5-miracle-millets-that-helped-a-67-yo-control-her-diabetes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ere-cropping%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%20(leaving%20six%20inches%20of%20stubble%20in%20the%20ground%20after%20harvest%